"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-01-french-cabbies-seek-payout-lost-olympics-revenue\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - French taxi drivers on Thursday demanded government compensation for lost revenue during the Olympic Games as traffic disruptions and fewer regular clients weigh on demand.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.866164299741999, \"rank\": 0.04500741401904562, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9769398683819137, \"rank\": 0.017832464768457002, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 15, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 45, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"government compensation\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 86}, {\"ngram\": \"lost revenue\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic disruptions\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 151}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer regular clients\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a letter to the transport ministry, taxi unions said that the Games had been \\\"hugely disappointing\\\" for the drivers of licensed taxis of which there are 20,000 in Paris alone.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transport\", \"score\": 0.9999999700391986, \"rank\": 2.996063226714313e-08, \"text\": \"transport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Transport\"}, {\"begin\": 362, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994682047195, \"rank\": 5.317954815195528e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"taxi unions\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 266}, {\"ngram\": \"the drivers\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"licensed taxis\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Demand is slowing and the entire profession is being prevented from simply doing their job because of these Games,\\\" said the letter, seen by AFP.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999991236419848, \"rank\": 8.589338701715912e-07, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Demand\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire profession\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"their job\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"the letter\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The number of additional visitors drawn by the Olympics had failed to make up for \\\"the impact of traffic restrictions, the closure of venues and the impact of usual customers staying away\\\", it said.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The number\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"additional visitors\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic restrictions\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"usual customers\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unions demanded the creation of a \\\"compensation fund\\\" that they said should cover income lost for the seven-month period during which public spaces were being taken over for the Games.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unions\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"compensation fund\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"income\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the seven-month period\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"public spaces\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several venues in and around Paris, but also in Marseille were blocked off for several weeks before the Games started on July 26.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994682047195, \"rank\": 5.317954815195528e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.7234978000389277, \"rank\": 0.38211427688515825, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several venues\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"several weeks\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to the letter, Transport Minister Patrice Vergriete said in a social media post that taxis and ride-hailing services would now be allowed to enter the so-called \\\"red zones\\\" around Olympics venues, which were previously off-limits for motor vehicles.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1072, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Transport\", \"score\": 0.8715569834745176, \"rank\": 0.14737190907873274, \"text\": \"Transport Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Transport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Secretary_of_State_for_Transport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the letter\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"a social media post\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"taxis\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"ride-hailing services\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the so-called \\\"red zones\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics venues\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"off-limits\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"motor vehicles\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that the high-security opening ceremony was in the past, several safety measures had been lifted and traffic was becoming more fluid, the minister said.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the high-security opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"several safety measures\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the minister\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government has encouraged French residents to go on holiday or work remotely during the Games, further dampening demand and contributing to a sharp fall in business compared to the same period in 2023, the unions said.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9769398683819137, \"rank\": 0.017832464768457002, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"holiday\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"further dampening demand\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"a sharp fall\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the same period\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the unions\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some drivers had seen their income fall by 40 or 50 percent, they said.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some drivers\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"their income\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"40 or 50 percent\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last month, trade groups said that Paris shops, restaurants, bars and clubs were facing an \\\"unprecedented slump in business and footfall\\\", blaming in part the \\\"heavy security measures\\\" during the Games.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994682047195, \"rank\": 5.317954815195528e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trade groups\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"clubs\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"unprecedented slump\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"footfall\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"heavy security measures\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1978}]}]}"